#

Oven-Baked Sweet Potato Chips

35 min
$5
150 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeVegan

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Snack

Tags:

SnackHealthyEasy

Description

Crunchy and delicious, these oven-baked sweet potato chips are a healthier alternative to traditional chips.

Ingredients

  • sweet potatoes: 2 large
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • paprika: 1/2 teaspoon
  • garlic powder: 1/2 teaspoon
